        "e9928fa6-a242-4f13-bc23-8dd1679fa10e": {
          "settings": {
            "answer": "<p>Simple Modern is an employee-owned Oklahoma based company whose mission statement is we exist to give generously. Our desire is to make 5-star products offering remarkable value so we can give to worthy organizations making the world a better place. To hear more please check out <a href=\"https://www.simplemodern.com/pages/giving\" title=\"Link to the Simple Modern About Us page\">https://www.simplemodern.com/pages/giving</a> for a video about us and more.</p>",
            "category": "Company",
            "question": "What kind of company is Simple Modern?"
          },
          "type": "question"
        },
        "faq_categories_XFz8AQ": {
          "settings": {
            "category-name": "Returns"
          },
          "type": "faqCategories"
        },
        "ffcc866e-1f90-407f-9d2b-ee12354f47d6": {
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "category-name": "Bags"
          },
          "type": "faqCategories"
        },
        "question_3XTMfM": {
          "settings": {
            "answer": "<p>If your order hasn’t arrived within the expected delivery window, start by checking your tracking link for updates. If it shows as delivered but you can’t find it, we recommend checking with neighbors or your local carrier. If you still can’t locate your package, please submit a shipping claim at <a href=\"https://claims.simplemodern.com\" title=\"https://claims.simplemodern.com\">claims.simplemodern.com</a> and our team will happy to help! </p>",
            "category": "Orders",
            "question": "What if my package is missing or delayed?"
          },
          "type": "question"
        },
        "question_7CFbfe": {
          "settings": {
            "answer": "<p>Personalized and custom products are made just for you, so they aren’t eligible for return or exchange. If your personalized item arrives damaged or defective, please reach out to our team and we’ll make it right.</p>",
            "category": "Returns",
            "question": "Can I return personalized or custom items?"
          },
          "type": "question"
        },
        "question_Dgfy3e": {
          "settings": {
            "answer": "<p>Most items purchased on simplemodern.com can be returned for a refund within <strong>90 days</strong> of purchase. To qualify, items must be unused and in their original packaging. Please note that <strong>personalized products</strong> and <strong>Canadian orders</strong> aren’t eligible for return. Large or frequent returns may also be subject to a restocking fee.</p>",
            "category": "Returns",
            "question": "Can I return my order?"
          },
          "type": "question"
        },
        "question_GUaAbL": {
          "settings": {
            "answer": "<p>You can make changes to your order within the first 30 minutes by clicking the blue <strong>Edit/View Order</strong> button in your order confirmation email. From there, you can update your payment method, add discount codes, change items, adjust quantities, and edit your shipping address. If you need to cancel, our AI assistant can help within the first hour after your order is placed. <strong>After that,</strong> <strong>cancellations aren’t guaranteed</strong> due to the backend systems we use to process orders quickly.</p>",
            "category": "Orders",
            "question": "Can I edit or cancel my order?"
          },
          "type": "question"
        },
        "question_JmAbBW": {
          "settings": {
            "answer": "<p>Refunds are processed once your return is dropped off and in transit back to us. You’ll receive an email confirming your refund around the same time you drop off your return. Depending on your bank, it may take 3–5 business days for the funds to appear in your account.</p>",
            "category": "Returns",
            "question": "When will I receive my refund?"
          },
          "type": "question"
        },
        "question_LriYKp": {
          "settings": {
            "answer": "<p>Yes! You can ship directly to your recipient by entering their address at checkout. We don’t include pricing information in any packages.<br/><br/>At this time, we don’t offer gift notes or messaging options, and we apologize for any inconvenience this may cause.</p>",
            "category": "Orders",
            "question": "Can I send my order as a gift?"
          },
          "type": "question"
        },
        "question_dqU6QJ": {
          "settings": {
            "answer": "<p>Visit our return policy page <a href=\"https://www.simplemodern.com/pages/return-and-refund-policy\" title=\"https://www.simplemodern.com/pages/return-and-refund-policy\">HERE</a></p>",
            "category": "Returns",
            "question": "How do I start a return?"
          },
          "type": "question"
        }
